{"tid":1478741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日同我入美食展做文宣！！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:51:25.000Z","uid":132886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b6b5aa9672c59b749324334ef3c870ced75e4bb","tid":1478741,"uid":132886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"小弟我做左幾年美食展promoter，今年缺錢所以都唔例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本來預計今晚人流應該會過左d去遮打花園，點知屌你仲旺過上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多一家大細同後生仔好似無撚左件事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日襯仲趕得切快d入黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡量用airdrop費事比人趕，美食展人流集中又流動得快，airdrop一粒鐘好過你搭十粒鐘地鐵，仲可以邊食邊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818我唔要見到咁撚多人行美食展呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63107af86bb068c38c543e0631f08deec645693a","tid":1478741,"uid":132886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f4559c9fd8aeb71021ffdd9402afd37830e11","tid":1478741,"uid":132886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48181a8ed9f42d74885de42edc83a4c0668ba04","tid":1478741,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cc4e84f08a747c8b90c7c997cd92593d1ba1ba","tid":1478741,"uid":132886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:48:46.000Z","msg"